oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Songwriter Session - Erin Enderlin and Alex Kline - 2017-11-04
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by singer songwriters Erin Enderlin and Alex Kline from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on November 4, 2017. Guest appearance by Judy Blank. Includes questions from the audience.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Erin Enderlin; Alex Kline; Judy Booth;
